## Endpoint & Host Forensics

Getting deep visibility into what's happening on individual hosts is critical for both detection and IR. [securonix](https://www.securonix.com/blog/improving-blue-team-threat-detection-with-enhanced-siem-telemetry/)

- **Sysmon** – Deep Windows event logging; massively increases fidelity for SIEM rules [linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/vistasec_blueteam-threathunting-cyberdefense-activity-7394746860034392064-eDOf)
- **Velociraptor** – Endpoint visibility and live digital forensics at scale [linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/vistasec_blueteam-threathunting-cyberdefense-activity-7394746860034392064-eDOf)
- **Falco** – Runtime security for containers and cloud workloads, essential if you're running Docker/K8s [linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/vistasec_blueteam-threathunting-cyberdefense-activity-7394746860034392064-eDOf)
- **Volatility / Autopsy** – Memory and disk forensics for post-incident reconstruction [cybernx](https://www.cybernx.com/blue-team-tools/)

